5 NEW SECTION. SECTION 4. PERMITS FOR PLATOONING. UPON APPLICATION AND WITH
6 GOOD CAUSE SHOWN, THE DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION OR ITS AGENTS MAY ISSUE A
7 SPECIAL PERMIT AUTHORIZING THE APPLICANT TO OPERATE OR MOVE A PLATOON ON A HIGHWAY
8 UNDER THE DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION'S JURISDICTION. A CARRIER RECEIVING A PERMIT
9 MUST HAVE PUBLIC LIABILITY PROPERTY DAMAGE INSURANCE FOR THE PROTECTION OF THE
10 TRAVELING PUBLIC AS A WHOLE.
11
